==============
IntegrityGuard
==============

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/integrityguard?label=PyPI
     :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/integrityguard
     :alt: PyPI current version

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/integrityguard?label=Downloads
